      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Y57.3 (mss. 2040, 2101, 2104, 2106, 2109, 4000, 4010, 4025, 4040, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4161):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            rāspīg ātaxš abrōxtan wāz pad ātaxš abrōz griftan zōt <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō zaōtā</em>. rāspīg <em>yō zaōtā</em>. zōt <em>aϑā ratuš</em>. tā <em>sraōšəm</em>.</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "The <em>rāspīg</em> should kindle the fire and, while he is kindling the fire, they should take the <em>wāz</em>. The <em>zōt</em> (shoud say) <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō zaōtā</em>.; 
            the <em>rāspīg</em>: <em>yō zaōtā</em> until <em>sraōšəm</em>.</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
